Id":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"f45bd96643","type":"paragraph","text":"八届十一中全会召开一周年》关于武斗的指示","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"85ccb25f00","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年八月）","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"7bdf578f4a","type":"paragraph","text":"对武斗不要看得太紧张，对形势不能看得太严重，不要急。那里有武斗，必然有后台，让他多表演一下，越表演越孤立，使群众看得更清楚，群众孤立他，就好办了。乱是暂时的，可以转化为好的。打架是支流，是暂时的支流。决不能转移斗争的大方向。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"817f7b0bcb","type":"paragraph","text":"对《中共中央、国务院、中央重委、中央交革小粗给煤炭工业战线职工的一","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"7a30fa7771","type":"paragraph","text":"封信》的批示和修改","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"5c9a7774b4","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年八月十六日）批示：已开，照办。","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"163faf3210","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东主要修改：","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"1fdbd5d5ac","type":"paragraph","text":"信的开头，“广大的职工群众们”一句是主席加的。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"d3fe6b0e70","type":"paragraph","text":"信的第七段，在“无产阶级革命派和革命职工必须把国家利签”一句后加了“工人阶级利签”只字。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"16d01174a9","type":"paragraph","text":"第八段“凡是坚持下去、坚持生产，做出成绩的职工，不论属于哪个群众组织或者未参加组织，都应当给予表扬和适当奖励。”整段都是主席新加进去的。","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"c369574753","type":"paragraph","text":"·323","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83"}],"page":{"id":"c0e9d062e2","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e558fcfe83","start":336,"end":336}},"maoquanji50":{"comments":[{"id":"2d52060c73","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"e558fcfe83","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇一是毛泽东对这封信的批示；本篇二是毛泽东作的主要修改。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0cf3b41a77","type":"paragraph","text":"信的第八段“凡是坚持下去、坚持生产，做出成绩的职工，不论属于哪个群众组织或者未参加组织，都应当给予表扬和适当奖励。整段都是主席新加进去的。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"2d52060c73","type":"paragraph","text":"已阅，照办。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"34283659d5","type":"title","text":"对《中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革小组给煤炭工业战线职工的一封信》的批示和修改！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"87280f94cb","type":"paragraph","text":"信的第七段，在“无产阶级革命派和革命职工必须把国家利益”一句后加了“工人阶级利益”几字。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"c2bf2103d5","type":"paragraph","text":"信的开头，“广大的职工群众们”一句是主席加的。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"e558fcfe83"},{"id":"cf52aa2ded","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"e558fcfe83"}],"page":{"id":"a73006bbd8","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"e558fcfe83","start":52,"end":52}}}},"__N_SSG":true}